(364,242,100,2,0,'194.199.224.110',1403690499,0,1,1,1,1,'','Install Serveur DHCP','[code:301mqawf]C&#58;\\Users\\Administrateur&#46;7IRELIDE&gt;oclist | find &quot;DHCP&quot;[/code:301mqawf]\n[quote:301mqawf]Non installé :DHCPServerCore[/quote:301mqawf]\n\n[code:301mqawf]C&#58;\\Users\\Administrateur&#46;7IRELIDE&gt;start /w ocsetup DHCPServerCore[/code:301mqawf]\n\n[code:301mqawf]C&#58;\\Users\\Administrateur&#46;7IRELIDE&gt;oclist | find &quot;DHCP&quot;[/code:301mqawf]\n[quote:301mqawf]    Installé :DHCPServerCore[/quote:301mqawf]\n\n[code:301mqawf]C&#58;\\Users\\Administrateur&#46;7IRELIDE&gt;net start DHCPServer[/code:301mqawf]\nL\'erreur système 1058 s\'est produite.\n[quote:301mqawf]\nLe service ne peut pas être démarré parce qu\'il est désactivé ou qu\'aucun périph\nérique activé ne lui est associé.\n[/quote:301mqawf]\n[code:301mqawf]C&#58;\\Users\\Administrateur&#46;7IRELIDE&gt;sc config dhcpserver start= auto[/code:301mqawf]\n[quote:301mqawf][SC] ChangeServiceConfig réussite(s)[/quote:301mqawf]\n\nC:\\Users\\Administrateur.7IRELIDE&gt;\n\n[code:301mqawf]&#91;quote&#93;C&#58;\\Users\\Administrateur&#46;7IRELIDE&gt;sc qc dhcpserver[/code:301mqawf]\n[quote:301mqawf][SC] QueryServiceConfig réussite(s)\n\nSERVICE_NAME: dhcpserver\n        TYPE               : 20  WIN32_SHARE_PROCESS\n        START_TYPE         : 2   AUTO_START\n        ERROR_CONTROL      : 1   NORMAL\n        BINARY_PATH_NAME   : C:\\Windows\\system32\\svchost.exe -k DHCPServer\n        LOAD_ORDER_GROUP   :\n        TAG                : 0\n        DISPLAY_NAME       : Serveur DHCP\n        DEPENDENCIES       : RpcSs\n                           : Tcpip\n                           : SamSs\n                           : EventLog\n                           : EventSystem\n        SERVICE_START_NAME : NT AUTHORITY\\NetworkService[/quote:301mqawf]\n\n[code:301mqawf]C&#58;\\Users\\Administrateur&#46;7IRELIDE&gt;net start DHCPServer[/code:301mqawf]\n[quote:301mqawf]Le service Serveur DHCP démarre....\nLe service Serveur DHCP a démarré.[/quote:301mqawf]\n\n\nC:\\Users\\Administrateur.7IRELIDE&gt;\n\n[code:301mqawf]C&#58;\\Users\\Administrateur&#46;7IRELIDE&gt;netsh dhcp sh server[/code:301mqawf]\n[quote:301mqawf]\n0 serveurs trouvés dans le service d\'annuaire :\n\n\nLa commande s\'est terminée correctement.\n[/quote:301mqawf]\n[code:301mqawf]C&#58;\\Users\\Administrateur&#46;7IRELIDE&gt;netsh dhcp add server SRV-CORE02&#46;7irelide&#46;noip&#46;me 192&#46;168&#46;1&#46;2[/code:301mqawf]\n[quote:301mqawf]\nAjout du serveur SRV-CORE02.7irelide.noip.me, 192.168.1.2\n\nLa commande s\'est terminée correctement.\n[/quote:301mqawf]\nC:\\Users\\Administrateur.7IRELIDE&gt;\n\n[code:301mqawf]C&#58;\\Users\\Administrateur&#46;7IRELIDE&gt;netsh sh server[/code:301mqawf]\n[quote:301mqawf]La commande suivante n\'a pas été trouvée : sh server.[/quote:301mqawf]\n\n[code:301mqawf]C&#58;\\Users\\Administrateur&#46;7IRELIDE&gt;netsh dhcp sh server[/code:301mqawf]\n\n[quote:301mqawf]1 serveurs trouvés dans le service d\'annuaire :\n\n        Serveur [srv-core02.7irelide.noip.me] Adresse [192.168.1.2] Emplacement\nservice d\'annuaire : cn=srv-core02.7irelide.noip.me\n\n\nLa commande s\'est terminée correctement.[/quote:301mqawf]\n\nC:\\Users\\Administrateur.7IRELIDE&gt;','1f61813ec6fb42b8aaeac5cc2928da5a',0,'gIA=','301mqawf',1,0,'',0,0,0,1,0,'',0),
